	* customize.jl (customize-spec): translate group names

	* sm-init.jl (sm-init): remove -clientId as well as
	--sm-client-id options from saved-command-line-args

	* tooltips.jl (tooltips-unmapped): remove tooltips when their
	window is unmapped

