	* make-theme.jl: image decls now have attributes

1999-12-31  John Harper  <john@dcs.warwick.ac.uk>

	* make-theme.jl, make-theme-preview.jl: initial support for GUI
	theme builder
	* sawmill-gaol.jl: make-theme is safe to call

